eplyTime":"2018-08-05T20:56:23.000Z","msg":"廚房？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:01:27.000Z","msg":"放在桌面上的電話忽視響起, 我把電話解鎖一看, 拉下通知欄：<br />\n你有一則新消息<br />\n來自 LIHKG 死毛全撕對你的主題作出回覆「廚房？」<br />\n我驚訝了一下, 對, 剛才就是從廚房回到睡房查看電話的信息<br />\n難道這是代表著什麼嗎? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a11942a4e402d8cadabb015208103c761285c01","tid":768934,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6bb3cc86850cca74b39111b52760c4b86403f71b","tid":768934,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T20:57:15.000Z","msg":"幾點返工？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:06:17.000Z","msg":"接下來再查看下一個的回覆「幾點返工？」<br />\n對了, 什麼是上班?  上班又有什麼的意思, 一想起要晚點便要回到公司進行勾心鬥角的權力遊行便心力交瘁了<br />\n把放在剛喝完的喜力空鑵壓扁, 然後回覆「九點」"},{"pid":"8929158cf5c5c2f0b67bfe4a5e8146aab49f8258","tid":768934,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a11942a4e402d8cadabb015208103c761285c01","tid":768934,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6bb3cc86850cca74b39111b52760c4b86403f71b","tid":768934,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T20:57:15.000Z","msg":"幾點返工？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:06:17.000Z","msg":"接下來再查看下一個的回覆「幾點返工？」<br />\n對了, 什麼是上班?  上班又有什麼的意思, 一想起要晚點便要回到公司進行勾心鬥角的權力遊行便心力交瘁了<br />\n把放在剛喝完的喜力空鑵壓扁, 然後回覆「九點」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:08:11.000Z","msg":"good one<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c8f940abea031486c5f0a9a2a8473a8a367996","tid":768934,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:08:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"c10f6cd2f7341ec117447948548ed40555b500e0","tid":768934,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:14:05.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"f06f2cba7fdaa6c1b7f23fa449f1eccdf1bb3149","tid":768934,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5554afdac62960136d8697df2da8bb22960d4411","tid":768934,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:01:24.000Z","msg":"我又係瞓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:14:28.000Z","msg":"再向下滑一下手機，看到一個來自比熊犬的回覆說「我又係瞓唔著」<br />\n嘿，我冷笑了一下，連登真的那裡多廢青啊，不睡的肯定都是在打 J 吧<br />\n股乳有暈: 不孝有三無圖為大，還要配上一面自豪的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 的表情符號<br />\n這個仆街仔肯定是收藏了不少高質的長腿高瘦索女 J 圖。<br />\n為了吸引他放出J圖, 我便引導式回覆了他「打轉飛機就訓得著 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},{"pid":"ae2829f8f233d35d08aeeba1e845eac354359138","tid":768934,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c10f6cd2f7341ec117447948548ed40555b500e0","tid":768934,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:14:05.000Z","msg":"雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:17:54.000Z","msg":"呢個回錯 唔洗理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44e717984591fb28ee671f14f422a7ce8b6d343","tid":768934,"uid":103414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:19:27.000Z","msg":"失眠點算好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca024906c899c73aa2b661375d77bd99f77fb2d","tid":768934,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c8f940abea031486c5f0a9a2a8473a8a367996","tid":768934,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:08:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:26:13.000Z","msg":"「屌你老母」一來回自濛的回覆<br />\n我想了一下，這樣無趣的回覆，跟得閒飲茶，早晨沒分別<br />\n每次上班除了跟同事說早晨便是說屌你老母<br />\n還是真的想肉體上屌我老母驅風嗎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n說開又說，早排實在太多屌你老母的信息，招聘很多 ptlm 去應付<br />\n若真的是想屌我老母的話，不知道他想屌我哪一個老母呢? <br />\n於是我便給他回覆:「想屌我邊個老母? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},{"pid":"83e135f754aca14dce847262cd3fc1d23a1c5542","tid":768934,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c44e717984591fb28ee671f14f422a7ce8b6d343","tid":768934,"uid":103414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:19:27.000Z","msg":"失眠點算好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:32:03.000Z","msg":"剛才有點困了差點兒睡著，回神過來便看到一個來自花樣年華2046的回覆「失眠點算好？」 <br />\n哈..我也是在失眠，但你卻在問我如何處理，要是我知道的話早就睡了，還會有空在連登發文?<br />\n我想唯一能做到的是跟我聊天吧，聊到看看哪個先睡著，不老實說我也差不多困了想睡了，但在此之前先給他一個回覆吧：「同我傾計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},{"pid":"17076e8c42f73f2c9b1aefdfc5d52a94f5513d13","tid":768934,"uid":169950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:33:21.000Z","msg":"好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e613a1682ed9d96d6f898540e4e6ed1776dc8f37","tid":768934,"uid":121555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:36:08.000Z","msg":"點樣先可以練到樓主你咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6bda774e834acf080cac6672f8ac4a61b6b707","tid":768934,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17076e8c42f73f2c9b1aefdfc5d52a94f5513d13","tid":768934,"uid":169950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:33:21.000Z","msg":"好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:44:49.000Z","msg":"一個收到來自KDB的回覆說「好肚餓」<br />\n對了, 想起早半小時前回覆死毛全撕的信息時我便在廚房煮食中, <br />\n食物落肚後, 肚餓的感覺早就不見了<br />\n肚餓便要吃東西，這是絕對的的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n與其在連登發回覆，倒不如先去進食? <br />\n為了鼓勵 KBD 進食, 便給他一個回覆「落樓下24小時M記買個餐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},{"pid":"ca2b39ed03e7129b719dadd81facd5c7456cb0f7","tid":768934,"uid":12908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:47:30.000Z","msg":"發夢夢見個ex，醒咗之後訓唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f3f9ef9c4936edc91ad98fe0b0f4183d2c964e","tid":768934,"uid":37064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:55:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0beca463bf9787669e8862e433c5ca5acc0edd2b","tid":768934,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e613a1682ed9d96d6f898540e4e6ed1776dc8f37","tid":768934,"uid":121555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:36:08.000Z","msg":"點樣先可以練到樓主你咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:57:00.000Z","msg":"差不多睡的時候收到來只北上(Kitakami)的回覆<br />\n看到北上這個字特別興奮了，可惜現在在大陸多正的骨妹也只會能提供飛機餐，她們說怕警察放蛇，但是明明香港人在接待處登記時有登記回鄉卡的，是人是鬼怎樣不會不清楚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對了，他說「點樣先可以練到樓主你咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」我有在痴線嗎?<br />\n聽說在青山的人只會說自己是正常的, 其他人才是痴線, 我想他就是這類人了, 這樣也能比我遇到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是很正接地給他一個回覆「你就痴線」"},{"pid":"6b07d1b35c7d36c835fa4fcfa51d4b9b635cf262","tid":768934,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T21:57:43.000Z","msg":"屋企廚房幾大？"},{"pid":"cbb67f97a39e0f6cbf7c1a27a3f8061690ad1cd0","tid":768934,"uid":142651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T22:06:21.000Z","msg":"時差都搞到我瞓唔着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc6e8acf024eb0c3e4e5899b3e247303c9d3b9d","tid":768934,"uid":157669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T22:07:42.000Z","msg":"樓主你好"}]}